<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4281:4300'>䷱鼎䷟恒䷸巽䷯井䷑蠱䷭升䷷旅䷽小過</span>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4300:4326'>離互體凡十六卦<span class='krp-note'>凡十六離相與坎/卦爻隂陽  對</span></span>
