<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4485:4504'>䷬萃䷋否䷽小過䷷旅䷞咸䷠遯䷮困䷅訟</span>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4504:4524'>䷐隨䷘无妄䷶豐䷝離䷰革䷌同人䷹兊䷉履</span>
